data.text: Hey Kat, you were just telling me about all the pros and cons of different renewable energies and you just got me thinking we're going to run out of oil in the next couple of decades. There's reports that say we're going to run out of oil in the next twenty years, but I'm guessing that in fifty years or a hundred years we really will run out and we'll need some sort of other energy source. What do you think's going to happen?
